    <title>Adding a picture from Media library doesn't show the thumbnail in editor</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Steps to repro:</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">- Go to Posts and tap New.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.3">- Tap in the editor and add new picture</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.4">- Tap on the option "Add from media library"</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.5">- Select one picture</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.6">- The app takes you back to the editor screen with a placeholder of the picture.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.7">- After a while the placeholder disappears, and a "white" picture is shown in the editor</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.8">(you can tap on the "white picture" and open the detail screen.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.9">You need to guess where the picture is)</sentence>
        </paragraph>
